abstract: Will Yahoo eventually get sold to Microsoft? And if so, for how much?
lead_paragraph: Will Yahoo eventually get sold to Microsoft? And if so, for how much?

abstract: The Internet Advertising Bureau is trying to rally small firms to block new regulations on online advertising. Meanwhile, Microsoft criticizes the Google-Yahoo ad partnership ahead of a Senate hearing Tuesday on the deal.
snippet: The Internet Advertising Bureau is trying to rally small firms to block new regulations on online advertising. Meanwhile, Microsoft criticizes the Google-Yahoo ad partnership ahead of a Senate hearing Tuesday on the deal.
lead_paragraph: At an ad-industry conference Wednesday morning, much of the buzz in the room was about today’s Commerce Committee hearings in Washington, about online advertising and privacy.

headline.main: Advertisers Bite Back at Regulators, and Microsoft Snipes at Google-Yahoo Deal
